NOTICE: This plugin code (extensions/oi-capability/) is MIT licensed.

The plugin USES — but does not INCLUDE or INCORPORATE — the open-interpreter
package (GNU Affero General Public License v3, Copyright Open Interpreter).
open-interpreter is installed on-demand into an isolated Python venv by the
bootstrap process (subprocess/venv_bootstrap.py). It communicates with this
plugin exclusively via JSON-RPC over subprocess stdio and is never imported
into the main process.

See NOTICE file for the full AGPL isolation explanation.
